description: Wyld Networks AB is a SE-based company operating in  industry. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm. The company went IPO on 2021-07-02. Wyld Networks AB is a Sweden-based wireless technology company. The firm develops and sells wireless technology solutions that enables affordable connectivity anywhere in the world, addressing the problems for businesses and people regarding the lack of global mobile network coverage. The solutions are mainly targeted to wireless connectivity for the Internet of Things (IoT) and people.
